645
00:37:47.709 --> 00:37:49.252
<i>Itu sangat mengejutkan.</i>

646
00:37:49.627 --> 00:37:51.129
<i>Sangat mengejutkan.</i>

647
00:37:51.462 --> 00:37:54.215
<i>Apakah ada saatnya keyakinanmu,</i>

648
00:37:54.299 --> 00:37:56.134
<i>kepercayaan agamamu berubah?</i>

